msg: There were may fixes needed to this file to solve AXISCPP-520.
I do not know why on earth this source file was this much broken.
As far as I could test, these fixes seem to have minimal sideeffects, however I admit that there is a risk.

I myself do not like the fixes I did here. However I had to live with these fixes as I wanted to minimize the side effects and for the very reason I did not want to change any other file (so that in case of problems a roll back would be trivial)
